<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Xpress Life Quote Builder | Ricky Rampersad Branch</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:     #07131f;
      --bg2:    #0d2137;
      --card:   #163553;
      --card2:  #1b3d61;
      --gold:   #efc24b;
      --gold2:  #dca530;
      --text:   #edf4fb;
      --muted:  #a9bbcf;
      --line:   rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      --teal:   #00C9A7;
      --teal2:  #00a589;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -20%, rgba(0,201,167,.08), transparent),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg2) 50%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 16px 120px;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp .5s ease both;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 64px; height: 64px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .header-text .kicker {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold2);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .header-text h1 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: clamp(20px, 5vw, 28px);
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .header-text p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    /* ── CARD ── */
    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--card), var(--card2));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      animation: fadeUp .45s ease both;
    }

    .card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay:.05s }
    .card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay:.1s }
    .card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay:.15s }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--teal);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .section-label::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(0,201,167,.2);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    /* ── TABS ── */
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.25);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .tab {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 11px 8px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .22s;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .tab.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,201,167,.2), rgba(0,201,167,.08));
      color: var(--teal);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.25);
    }

    /* ── PERSON BLOCK ── */
    .person-block {
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .person-block.p1 {
      background: rgba(239,194,75,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239,194,75,.15);
    }

    .person-block.p2 {
      background: rgba(0,201,167,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.15);
    }

    .person-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .avatar.gold { background: rgba(239,194,75,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(239,194,75,.25); }
    .avatar.teal { background: rgba(0,201,167,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.25); }

    .person-head-info strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .person-head-info span {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── GRID ── */
    .grid2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .grid3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }

    @media(max-width:600px) {
      .grid2, .grid3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sa-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr) !important; }
    }

    /* ── FORM CONTROLS ── */
    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .8px;
    }

    select, input[type="text"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.3);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      appearance: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }

    select:focus, input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgba(0,201,167,.4);
    }

    /* ── SA CARDS ── */
    .sa-section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .sa-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5,1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .sa-card {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 11px 5px;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .18s;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      user-select: none;
    }

    .sa-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,201,167,.35);
      background: rgba(0,201,167,.06);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .sa-card.sel {
      border-color: var(--teal);
      background: rgba(0,201,167,.12);
    }

    .sa-card .amt {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .sa-card.sel .amt { color: var(--teal); }

    .sa-card .lbl {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
    }

    /* ── PAYMENT MODE ── */
    .mode-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    @media(max-width:600px) { .mode-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

    .mode-card {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 8px;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .18s;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      user-select: none;
    }

    .mode-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(239,194,75,.35);
      background: rgba(239,194,75,.05);
    }

    .mode-card.sel {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(239,194,75,.1);
    }

    .mode-card .mode-name {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .mode-card.sel .mode-name { color: var(--gold); }

    .mode-card .mode-save {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    /* ── RESULT PANEL ── */
    .result-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #061a14, #0a2318);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .result-panel::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 200px; height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,201,167,.1), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .result-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .result-premium {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 52px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--teal);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .result-premium-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .result-meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    @media(max-width:580px) { .result-meta { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

    .meta-item {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }

    .meta-item .ml {
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .meta-item .mv {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ── DEATH BENEFIT ROWS ── */
    .db-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .db-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr auto;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .db-row.yr1 { background: rgba(248,113,113,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.15); }
    .db-row.yr2 { background: rgba(239,194,75,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(239,194,75,.15); }
    .db-row.yr3 { background: rgba(0,201,167,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.15); }

    .db-yr { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; }
    .db-yr1 { color: #f87171; }
    .db-yr2 { color: var(--gold); }
    .db-yr3 { color: var(--teal); }
    .db-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .db-amt { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

    /* ── JOINT COMBINED BOX ── */
    .joint-combined {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,201,167,.14), rgba(0,201,167,.05));
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.3);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .jc-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .jc-amount {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 46px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--teal);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .jc-sub {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .jc-stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .jc-stat .jcs-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .jc-stat .jcs-val { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* ── PERSON SUMMARY CARDS (joint) ── */
    .p-summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    @media(max-width:500px) { .p-summary-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .p-summary {
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .p-summary.ps1 { background: rgba(239,194,75,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(239,194,75,.18); }
    .p-summary.ps2 { background: rgba(0,201,167,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.18); }

    .ps-name { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .ps-name.c1 { color: var(--gold); }
    .ps-name.c2 { color: var(--teal); }
    .ps-details { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .ps-prem { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; }
    .ps-prem.c1 { color: var(--gold); }
    .ps-prem.c2 { color: var(--teal); }
    .ps-cover { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; }

    /* ── FEATURES ── */
    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 7px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }

    .feat {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 5px 11px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── CALLOUT BOX ── */
    .callout {
      background: rgba(239,194,75,.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(239,194,75,.18);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .callout b { color: var(--gold); }

    .callout-teal {
      background: rgba(0,201,167,.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,201,167,.18);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .callout-teal b { color: var(--teal); }

    /* ── APPLY NOW BUTTON ── */
    .apply-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--teal2));
      color: #021a14;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all .2s;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,201,167,.3);
    }

    .apply-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0,201,167,.45);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00dbb8, var(--teal));
    }

    .apply-btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .apply-btn .apply-arrow {
      font-size: 20px;
      transition: transform .2s;
    }

    .apply-btn:hover .apply-arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

    .apply-note {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* ── OVERVIEW SECTION ── */
    .overview-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    @media(max-width:600px) { .overview-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .ov-item {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .ov-icon {
      font-size: 22px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .ov-title {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .ov-desc {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .health-q-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .health-q-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(248,113,113,.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.12);
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .health-q-list li .qnum {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #f87171;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
      min-width: 20px;
    }

    .collapse-btn {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: var(--teal);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── BOTTOM BAR ── */
    .bar {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(6,17,29,.97);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      padding: 12px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 100;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .bar-left .bar-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .bar-left .bar-total { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--teal); }

    .bar-right { text-align: right; }
    .bar-right .bar-daily { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
    .bar-right .bar-cover { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; margin-top: 2px; }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .result-panel { animation: fadeUp .3s ease both; }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .divider { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); margin: 18px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="header">
    <svg class="logo" viewBox="0 0 88 88" aria-hidden="true">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="g1" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f0c448"/>
          <stop offset="60%" stop-color="#c9942c"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7a5810"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <path d="M44 5L77 19V41C77 63 63 76 44 83C25 76 11 63 11 41V19Z" fill="url(#g1)"/>
      <path d="M28 44L39 55L60 31" stroke="#07131f" stroke-width="7" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M28 44L39 55L60 31" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="header-text">
      <div class="kicker">Ricky Rampersad Branch</div>
      <h1>Xpress Life Quote Builder</h1>
      <p>Instant issue · No medicals · 5 health questions · Individual or couple</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PRODUCT OVERVIEW -->
  <div class="card" style="animation-delay:.08s">
    <button class="collapse-btn" onclick="toggleOverview(this)">
      <span id="ovArrow">▼</span> What is Xpress Life? — Product Overview
    </button>
    <div id="overviewContent">

      <div class="overview-grid">
        <div class="ov-item">
          <div class="ov-icon">⚡</div>
          <div>
            <div class="ov-title">Instant Issue — No Medicals</div>
            <div class="ov-desc">No blood tests, no doctor visits. Just 5 health questions. If all answers are No, the policy is approved immediately.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ov-item">
          <div class="ov-icon">🛡️</div>
          <div>
            <div class="ov-title">Whole Life Coverage</div>
            <div class="ov-desc">Coverage lasts to age 100. Premiums are paid for 20 years only — then coverage continues for free for the rest of your life.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ov-item">
          <div class="ov-icon">💰</div>
          <div>
            <div class="ov-title">Sum Assured Options</div>
            <div class="ov-desc">Choose TT$100,000 · $200,000 · $300,000 · $400,000 or $500,000. Maximum total Xpress Life coverage per person is $500,000.</div>
          </div>
